Wrap pages with KeepAlive and hide with opacity/visibility instead of conditional render.

Add custom React.memo comparator for Window (only re-render on real prop changes).

Make sure movement uses transform via CSS variables + rAF.

Persist animation-seen state by windowId.

Use profiler + comparator logs to find any remaining unstable prop.

